#. <section class="sutta" id="sn18.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn18.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 18"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 18"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn18.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Rūpasutta → rūpādiārammaṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn18.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Rūpasutta"
msgstr "2. Sights, Etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.246"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn18.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rāhula, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Rāhula? "

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.3"
msgid "rūpā niccā vā aniccā vā”ti?"
msgstr "Are sights permanent or impermanent?”"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.4"
msgid "“Aniccā, bhante” … pe …"
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.5"
msgid "saddā …"
msgstr "“… sounds …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.6"
msgid "gandhā …"
msgstr "smells …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.7"
msgid "rasā …"
msgstr "tastes …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.8"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbā …"
msgstr "touches …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.9"
msgid "dhammā niccā vā aniccā vā”ti?"
msgstr "Are thoughts permanent or impermanent?”"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.10"
msgid "“Aniccā, bhante” …"
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.11"
msgid ""
"“evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpesupi nibbindati … saddesupi "
"nibbindati … gandhesupi nibbindati … rasesupi nibbindati … phoṭṭhabbesupi "
"nibbindati … dhammesupi nibbindati;"
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with sights, "
"sounds, smells, tastes, touches, and thoughts."

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.12"
msgid "nibbindaṃ virajjati … pe …"
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. …”"

msgctxt "sn18.2:1.13"
msgid "pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn18.2:1.14"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
